title: I am Kawehi
description: I just really liked it, I didn't want it to disappear because not enough of us have good taste. The internet in a lot of ways is being censored not by Big Brother, by the evils of convenience, impatience, wasted time. There are those who are in a position to make this phenomenon work for them and I say God bless them for it. I don't care what medium or what ideology you follow.
